install Ipopt

install QPSolvers project

set the environment variables QORE_ROOT_DIR and QPOASES_ROOT_DIR to the base directories where the solvers are installed.  At this point, it is assumed that the compilation was done in "build" subdirectories.

set environment variables
IPOPT_ROOT_DOR : base dir of the Ipopt installation, i.e., where the 'lib' subdirectory is
PKG_CONFIG_PATH=${IPOPT_ROOT_DIR}/lib/pkgconfig:$PKG_CONFIG_PATH
